### Post-doc / Research-Scientist

While we don't currently have funding for a full-time position we're always interested in hearing from interested folks. There are always [unexpected opportunities](https://eshinjolly.com/2021/05/03/delightful-journey/) to explore new research directions, funding avenues, and learn/develop new methods together.

